features: WOOD LACING FRUIT TOY - Wooden Lacing Big Apple Toy is a new kind of learning toy for Toddler. This Apple lacing toy is an exceptional gift for boys and girls.

IDEAL FOR PRACTICING FINE-MOTOR DEVELOPMENT - Doing traditional teaching Montessori activities helps to inspire children and develop lacing and sewing skills, strengthen their fine-motor skills and hand-eye coordination, while encouraging independence.

ATTRACTIVE DESIGN - A cute wooden caterpillar is connected to the apple toy by a 30-inch lacing string. When children thread the string through the holes of the apple, it looks like the caterpillar is "eating" the apple. Kids will love getting busy with this Montessori lacing toy!
STURDY WOOD TOY - Lacing big apple is made of high quality wood with non-toxic water paint, no chemical smell, up to safety standard EN71.

SIZE & RECOMMENDED AGES - 5.91 x 5.51 x 1.02 inch,easy for small hands to hold and play. Perfect Christmas Gift / Birthday Gift. And it is also large enough to prevent accidental swallow.Suitable toy for 3 years old and up.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 22, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Purchased for my 2 year old, as an airplane activity. Unfortunately she wasn’t interested, but the toy is durable, well made, and performs as described!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 21, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Nice! If only my toddler agreed…
reviews.reviewText: Cute and creative! We’ll-made. No issues with the product itself. I’m tempted to play with it actually! But my 2.5 year old boy was not too thrilled. It’s hit or miss with him with toys anyways, so I’m not entirely surprised. It is a little on the heavy side, but only as much to be expected due to being made of wood. I’ll save it for my daughter and see what she thinks when she is old enough to play with it.5 stars cause companies can’t control a toddler’s opinions (then again, who can?)

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 11, 2023
reviews.reviewText: This gorgeous toy is high quality and sturdy. Great wooden toy in vivid colors. My 2 year old isn’t super interested in it for more than 2 minutes but it’s a great item for what it is.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 11, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Great toy except
reviews.reviewText: So this thing is NICE. It's sturdy. It's heavy. It's well made. It can be used as a weapon. My toddler will weave that little worm through until he's out of string and then come swing it at us to help unwind it. I have bruises. My infant has bruises. This thing is being put away until we are past the "hitting people with things" phase because it's just too sturdy. But it is exactly as advertised

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on March 10, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Well made and looks pretty
reviews.reviewText: This lacing toy is very well made and sturdy. The colors are bright and overall, as an adult, i find it to be visually appealing. With that being said, i decided not to keep it for two reasons. 1. It is pretty heavy and bulky. You can see the thickness of it in the picture and it is solid wood. I was going to pack it as a travel toy, however when you have limited space in your diaper bag, you are forced to be picky about the items you bring. 2. My toddler just didn't seem to care about it, maybe because he is a little too young for it (21 months). We might repurchase when he is older.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 20, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars One of the faves!
reviews.reviewText: My child loves this product so much!!! He has been playing with it the last 6 months or so (12-18 months old) and still isn’t tired of it! It’s a great toy if your kids loves puzzles and also if they love playing with stringed toys.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 31, 2023
reviews.reviewText: My 18 month old was slightly too young for this but will grow in to using it! Great quality and color if you aren't in to all the bright, noisy toys for toddlers.
